dc.title: United States Court of Appeals for the Federal Circuit | Official Website
dc.description: Federal Circuit opinions, decisions, rules, calendars, notices and jobs. The Federal Circuit is one of the 13 U.S. Courts of Appeals, with jurisdiction over appeals from the Court of Federal Claims, patent appeals from U.S. district courts, and appeals from the MSPB, the Court of Appeals for Veterans Claims, and other boards and tribunals.
